These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, cola, iced-tea, almond-milk, water, milk
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, indonesian, malaysian, canadian, american, indian, colombian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, climbing, cycling, rugby, ice-hockey, badminton, snowboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, boat, helicopter, snowmobile, skateboard, roller, tram
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the canadian##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the colombian##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the american##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the tram and the indian##2
 9. the american is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the scooter##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the malaysian##1
14. the indian is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the colombian##1
16. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
17. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the malaysian##1
18. the person drinking milk is on the right of the american##1
19. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | water        | almond-milk | cola      | iced-tea     | mirinda      | milk     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | canadian         | colombian   | russian | indian    | american | malaysian |
